\v 6 \w Run|strong="H1980"\w*! \w Run|strong="H1980"\w*! \w Run|strong="H1980"\w* \w away|strong="H1980"\w* \w from|strong="H1980"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* northern land, says \w the|strong="H7200"\w* Lord, because \w I|strong="H7200"\w* \w have|strong="H7200"\w* scattered \w you|strong="H7200"\w* \w to|strong="H1980"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* four winds \w of|strong="H7341"\w* heaven.
