\v 8 \w For|strong="H3427"\w* \w this|strong="H1696"\w* \w is|strong="H3389"\w* \w what|strong="H1696"\w* \w the|strong="H8432"\w* Lord Almighty \w said|strong="H1696"\w*: Afterwards \w the|strong="H8432"\w* glorious Lord\f + \fr 2:8 \ft “Afterwards the glorious Lord”: Hebrew unclear. Literally, “after glory.”\f* sent \w me|strong="H1696"\w* \w against|strong="H1696"\w* \w the|strong="H8432"\w* nations \w that|strong="H5288"\w* plundered \w you|strong="H8432"\w*—\w for|strong="H3427"\w* \w those|strong="H1696"\w* \w who|strong="H3427"\w* touch \w you|strong="H8432"\w* touch \w the|strong="H8432"\w* apple \w of|strong="H3427"\w* \w his|strong="H8432"\w* eye.
