\p 
\v 10 Sing \w in|strong="H3068"\w* celebration, people \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w Zion|strong="H6566"\w*, \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w am|strong="H3068"\w* coming \w to|strong="H3068"\w* live \w with|strong="H3068"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w*, \w declares|strong="H5002"\w* \w the|strong="H5002"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w*.
\v 11 Many nations \w will|strong="H1323"\w* become believers\f + \fr 2:11 \ft “Become believers”: literally, “join themselves.”\f* \w in|strong="H3427"\w* Lord \w on|strong="H3427"\w* \w that|strong="H4422"\w* day, \w and|strong="H3427"\w* they \w shall|strong="H1323"\w* \w be|strong="H6726"\w* \w my|strong="H4422"\w* \w people|strong="H3427"\w*. I \w will|strong="H1323"\w* \w live|strong="H3427"\w* \w among|strong="H3427"\w* \w you|strong="H6726"\w*, \w and|strong="H3427"\w* \w you|strong="H6726"\w* \w will|strong="H1323"\w* know \w the|strong="H3427"\w* Lord Almighty \w has|strong="H6726"\w* sent me \w to|strong="H1323"\w* \w you|strong="H6726"\w*.
